extends pug/layout

block main
        include pug/database
        include pug/mixin
        section.poster 
            .container-fluid.position-relative.poster__img   
                img(src="./img/bg-1.png")
                .poster__img-name.position-absolute 
                    h1
                        span the movie
                        span film
                .poster__img-mountain.position-absolute  
                    img(src="img/bg-2.png")
                each n,index in Array(8)
                    .position-absolute.poster__img-cloud(data-count=index)
                        img(src="img/cloud-layer-1.png")
        section.about
            .container
                .text-center.about__title 
                    i.fas.fa-align-center 
                    h3.mt-3.text-uppercase.font-weight-bold about the movie
                .row.mt-5 
                    .py-5.col-sm-12.col-lg-4.about__img 
                        img(src="img/ab-m-1.png")
                    .col-sm-12.col-lg-8.about__info 
                        h4.text-uppercase.font-weight-bold.about__info-sub fantastic,history,war 
                        h1.mt-3.text-capitalize.font-weight-bold.about__info-title the beginning of new life 
                        .mt-5.about__info-list
                            .d-flex.align-items-center.about__info-item
                                p 
                                    i.fas.fa-play-circle.mr-3
                                    h4.text-capitalize.text-secondary.font-weight-bold production: 
                                h5.ml-5.text-muted January 15, 2006 - France, United States
                            .d-flex.align-items-center.about__info-item
                                p 
                                    i.fas.fa-clock.mr-3
                                    h4.text-capitalize.text-secondary.font-weight-bold time: 
                                h5.ml-5.text-muted 2 hours, 40 minutes
                            .d-flex.align-items-center.about__info-item
                                p 
                                    i.fas.fa-language.mr-3
                                    h4.text-capitalize.text-secondary.font-weight-bold Language: 
                                h5.ml-5.text-muted English, Spanish
                            .d-flex.align-items-center.about__info-item
                                p 
                                    i.fas.fa-globe-americas.mr-3
                                    h4.text-capitalize.text-secondary.font-weight-bold country: 
                                h5.ml-5.text-muted France, England, United States
                            .d-flex.align-items-center.about__info-item
                                p 
                                    i.fas.fa-briefcase.mr-3
                                    h4.text-capitalize.text-secondary.font-weight-bold company: 
                                h5.ml-5.text-muted Sxop, TLVR, Punctpro
                            .d-flex.align-items-center.about__info-item
                                p 
                                    i.fas.fa-check-square.mr-3
                                    h4.text-capitalize.text-secondary.font-weight-bold Distributor: 
                                h5.ml-5.text-muted O Production 
                        h4.mt-5.text-muted.about__info-decription  Nullam imperdiet, sem at fringilla lobortis, sem nibh fringilla nibh, id gravida mi purus sit amet erat. Ut dictum nisi massa, vitae pulvinar metus scelerisque in. Nunc sit amet purus at eros semper mattis. Donec a neque a velit dignissim euismod. Nulla facilisi. Phasellus pharetra felis mollis egestas suscipit. Integer in quam orci. Donec ornare aliquet diam nec malesuada.Sed iaculis malesuada aliquam. Nullam eu lobortis magna, nec accumsan orci. Cras a faucibus velit. Donec vehicula accumsan lectus, et venenatis eros ultrices et.  
